422
00:23:33,495 --> 00:23:35,546
RUSSELL COTTRELL: So what are you gonna do?

423
00:23:35,651 --> 00:23:37,528
JOYCE COTTRELL: What am I gonna do?

424
00:23:37,632 --> 00:23:39,578
She's our daughter.

425
00:23:39,682 --> 00:23:41,142
RUSSELL COTTRELL: Yeah, but you're

