00:27:40,687 --> 00:27:41,800
Hi.

521
00:27:41,904 --> 00:27:44,788
This is, uh, Dawn, the girl I told you about.

522
00:27:44,893 --> 00:27:46,944
Hi, Dawn.

523
00:27:47,047 --> 00:27:48,264
